<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Zzule:
[B]When I was around 20th, I was grouped in Najena with some friends.  We had been there all night and I needed to bank badly.  So I gated to town and promptly fell asleep on my keyboard.  I woke up a couple hours later with computer keys plastered to my face and still grouped!  They sure had a laugh when they realized what had happened.  They had been talking to me and each other the whole time apparently and thought I was mad at them for some reason they could not fathom. 

More recently, my husband bought me flowers and since we were eq'ing, I wanted them next to the computer so I could see them.  So the group pulls, and my sweet little kitty decided to have a taste of the 'salad bar' on my desk.  Just as we pulled, she knocked the vase over onto my keyboard and mouse, which stopped working entirely.  So there I am frantically shouting at my husband to tell the group I cant heal them and he is laughing at me trying to dry out my keyboard and at the way the cat charged out of the room with wet feet. 

I had to do the whole keyboard switcharound since the bath drowned it.  I dont think anyone died but they all laughed. ;P

Zzule D`Aemon [/B][/QUOTE]

